    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Mirror contacts across systems with HubSpot and Google Drive hands-free\n\n**Pattern:** Two-System Sync · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nMirror contacts across systems with HubSpot and Google Drive hands-free. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual contact sync is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nDaily Schedule → Map to Canonical Schema → Route by Event Kind → Handle 'created' → HubSpot → Consolidate Handling → Guard Non-Empty email → Align Field Names → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to two-system sync without manual effort\n- Anyone automating contact sync in sales\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Improves response time\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n- Responds in seconds\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: HubSpot private-app token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -830,
        80
      ],
      "id": "6425c769-206e-1156-3618-7abc602e125e",
      "name": "📘 Workflow Overview"
    },
